name: Atteli
tag_list: intranet, crm, workflow, dms, inventory-management, knowledge-management
overview:
Atteli provides support in change management within a business and strengthens effects related to implementation of modern communication tools and technologies in business. We aim to ensure our customers? implementation is conducted properly and swiftly, with rational costs and minimum risk maintained.

We complement our customers? knowledge regarding implementation of new technologies in business. We provide aid in choosing the optimal solution, we suggest methods for cooperating with subcontractors and specifying tasks and objectives for employees involved in projects of this sort.

We provide our services to organizations which face modernization of internal communication or which are in a pre-implementation stage, or even those that already have carried out the implementation and need support in effective implementation of changes within the company.
